          "reviewBody": "Very good, my daughter love and she is  having a good progress every year.\nI loved everything about this school. My daughter is happy and thriving. Plenty of volunteer opportunities for parents too. Welcoming environment for the parents as well! Teachers are dedicated to their duties and take pride in their students’ achievements. This school is definitely all around a 5/5.",
          "publisher": {
