          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "A very good English Medium school run by missionaries of charity at a very good location\nin the heart of the city on main GT road opposite Opulent Mall and comprising of very vast campus. Apart from normal students there\nare deaf & dumb students also. There is separate building/ area for deaf & dumb students. A very old but maintained building the school has for the administrative block and few other buildings are also old but one three story building appears to be added a few years back. A very good amount of students are studying here in this school and alone in the deaf & dumb section there are approximately\n300 students. A good school in the heart of the city.",
